-- Burda Sees Magazine Sales Growth, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 2012-04-11T17:24:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-11/burda-sees-magazine-sales-growth-handelsblatt-reports.html
German media group Hubert Burda
Media Holding GmbH & Co. plans to increase magazine sales by 25
percent over the next four years, Handelsblatt reported, citing
an interview with Burkhard Grassmann, head of the company’s news
group.  Burda will boost digital sales to reach that goal, the
newspaper said in a preview of an article for tomorrow’s
edition.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karin Matussek in Berlin at 
